<%= turbo_stream.prepend "quotes" do %>
  <%= render @quote %>
<% end %>

<%= turbo_stream.update Quote.new, "" %>

<%#
  The first line tells Turbo to prepend the app/views/quotes/_quote.html.erb to the Turbo Frame with id `quotes`.
  The second line tells Turbo to update the Turbo Frame with id new_quote with empty content. - This will clear the form.
%>

<%#
In Rails
`render partial: "quotes/quote", locals: { quote: @quote }`
and
`render @quote`
are equivalent.
%>

